questionResult_name: Will Your Lover Cheat On You

answersResultList.title: Your lover is loyal.
answersResultList.resultContent: Everyone has a past. We all have weak moments or make mistakes. But when your sweetie says you're the only one, you believe him or her. After all, don't you appreciate other people's beauty and like conversing with interesting strangers? It's normal for social animals. And yours will always come when you whistle, so there's no need for that leash!
